<view class="container">
  <!-- 背景装饰 -->
  <view class="bg-decoration">
    <view class="bg-circle circle-1"></view>
    <view class="bg-circle circle-2"></view>
    <view class="bg-circle circle-3"></view>
  </view>

  <!-- 悬浮粒子效果 -->
  <view class="particles">
    <view class="particle" wx:for="{{20}}" wx:key="index"></view>
  </view>

  <view class="header">
    <view class="header-icon">🔥</view>
    <text class="title">哑巴会 · 小游戏合集</text>
    <text class="subtitle">选择一个关卡开始体验彝族文化</text>
    <view class="title-underline"></view>
  </view>

  <view class="game-list">
    <!-- 关卡一：祭拜神树 -->
    <view class="game-card card-1" bindtap="goToGame1">
      <view class="card-decoration"></view>
      <view class="game-icon">🌳</view>
      <view class="game-content">
        <view class="game-title-row">
          <text class="game-title">关卡一 · 祭拜神树</text>
          <text class="game-tag">记忆 + 点击</text>
        </view>
        <text class="game-desc">
          记住祭祀顺序，按步骤点亮香火、酒水、贡品和经幡，完成对神树的祭拜仪式。
        </text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-arrow">→</view>
    </view>

    <!-- 关卡二：恭请大哑巴 -->
    <view class="game-card card-2" bindtap="goToGame2">
      <view class="card-decoration"></view>
      <view class="game-icon">👤</view>
      <view class="game-content">
        <view class="game-title-row">
          <text class="game-title">关卡二 · 恭请大哑巴</text>
          <text class="game-tag game-tag-secondary">装扮 + 顺序</text>
        </view>
        <text class="game-desc">
          按正确顺序为大哑巴绘制龙纹、佩戴牛皮头饰与野鸡羽毛，手持法器，准备开启仪式。
        </text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-arrow">→</view>
    </view>

    <!-- 关卡三：吉祥入户 -->
    <view class="game-card card-3" bindtap="goToGame3">
      <view class="card-decoration"></view>
      <view class="game-icon">🏮</view>
      <view class="game-content">
        <view class="game-title-row">
          <text class="game-title">关卡三 · 吉祥入户</text>
          <text class="game-tag game-tag-tertiary">节奏 + 资源</text>
        </view>
        <text class="game-desc">
          扮演大哑巴或随行助手，进入村民家中完成“驱邪 → 纳福 → 受礼”的传统流程。
        </text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-arrow">→</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 底部文化说明 -->
  <view class="footer">
    <text class="footer-text">彝族火把节传统文化体验</text>
  </view>
</view>
